@title    Vault interface
 @notice   The interface for functions Vault implements

getKeyManager().notice: Get the KeyManager address/interface that's used to validate sigs

suspend().notice: Can be used to suspend contract execution - only executable by          governance and only to be used in case of emergency.

updateKeyManager((address,uint256,uint25.notice: Update KeyManager reference. Used if KeyManager contract is updated

params.sigData: The keccak256 hash over the msg (uint) (here that's normally                  a hash over the calldata to the function with an empty sigData) and                  sig over that hash (uint) from the aggregate key

natspec.notice: The interface for functions Vault implements
natspec.title: Vault interface
